activities.message:
Hi @ag3nt-s21,

Please see as follows:

1. Create a █████████ package. For convenience, you may log into one I've created at██████/StatusLogIn.aspx?PackageID=15741848 with password `███████`
2. Scroll to the bottom. Add your own email under the `Add New Recipient` section and intercept the request to `POST /████/Status.aspx?ID=15741848` in Burp Suite to submit the form:

    {F366694}

    {F366695}

3. Modify the `ID` parameter in the url of the request to `15743188`, a different package that I created for testing purposes.
4. Observe that if the email address has not already been invited, you will see the following in the response:

    {F366697}

5. The package will be shared with your email address, which can then be downloaded as normal.
